pages.text:
About Us
Lighthouse Cove is a tropical fishing village-themed,
36-hole miniature golf course
featuring dramatic sea life, boats, waterfalls, caves and more. Come explore the history of Jupiter while playing on our two courses.
One block from the beautiful beaches of Jupiter, in Palm Beach, we offer
premium burgers
with our special blend, served with our secret Surf Sauce at
The Burger Shack
at Lighthouse Cove. Come celebrate your corporate event, birthday party or a day of family-fun.
Don’t forget to check out our premium ice cream, milkshakes and more at
3 Scoops
!
Adult refreshments are available on and off the course with regional craft beers and a selection of wines.
Our Jupiter location is just 20 minutes from West Palm Beach and Palm Beach International Airport.
.entry-content

Corporate/Team Building
Schedule Event
Corporate and Non-Corporate Groups/Company Picnics/Team Building/Celebrations/Holiday Parties/Family and Class Reunions/Events
Corporate (and of course, non corporate)
teambuilding events include mini golf, beer & wine, food and more!
Come with your team to explore 18 or 36 holes of our world class, tropical miniature golf course, lush landscaping and Caribbean/Key West style music. We will serve beverages directly to your golf hole or join us for our special blend burgers, fries and shakes at
The Burger Shack
.
Our Jupiter location is just 1 block from the beach on A1A and just 20 minutes away from West Palm Beach in Palm Beach County.
CLICK HERE
to our events team for more information.
